[Result "*"]

1. d4 d5 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. e3 e6 4. Bd3 b6 5. O-O Bb7 6. Nbd2 Bd6 7. b3 O-O 8. Bb2
Nbd7 9. Ne5 Ne4 10. f4 { White has other tries. } 10... f6 11. Nxe4 dxe4 12.
Bc4 { A great idea, sacrificing a piece. } 12... fxe5 13. Bxe6+ Kh8 14. dxe5
Bc5 15. Re1
{ Chessable: White protects the foundation of his central structure and plans to attack the kingside starting with Qd1-g4 and f4-f5-f6.  Full Theoretical Overiew }
