{ The next plan is to go h3 and g4, making the f5-pawn a target. } 18... Bxe5
19. dxe5 Nd7 20. f4 c4 21. Be2 b5 22. b4
{ Taking control of the c5-square while intending Bd4 followed by g4. } *

